name: Eliana Elliot
author: EmmaSiren
description: Eliana loves reading and writing stories. She has 4 younger siblings.

name: Hana Elliot
author: EmmaSiren
description: Hana loves all things girly, shopping, and playing pranks on people with her triplet brothers.

name: Damian Elliot
author: EmmaSiren
description: Damian is quiet and reserved but enjoys causing a ruckus with his siblings. He is a triplet.

name: Jay Darcy Elliot
author: EmmaSiren
description: JD is the timid and nervous one of the family. He doesn't like pulling pranks on people but his siblings pull him into their shenanigans.
